    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the CFD hemolysis model for the CPB COU based on satisfactory performance of 10 assessed credibility factors, all meeting or exceeding required levels for MRL 3. Three factors (numerical solver error, use error, equivalency of input parameters) were not assessed, with rationale citing resource constraints and scope limitations. The team concluded that the assessed factors collectively provide sufficient evidence for the intended decision, though the unassessed factors represent acknowledged gaps in the credibility argument.",
